[0m[49m[39m  130, 132[0m:[39m[49m flowchart TD
[0m[49m[39m  131, 133[0m:[39m[49m     A[Clinical Note\nFinalized in EHR] -->|Event| B[Lambda\nPipeline Orchestrator]
[0m[49m[39m  132, 134[0m:[39m[49m     B -->|DetectEntitiesV2| C[Amazon\nComprehend Medical]
[0m[49m[39m  133, 135[0m:[39m[49m     C -->|Entities + Traits| B
[0m[49m[39m  134, 136[0m:[39m[49m     B -->|Entity + Context| D[SageMaker Endpoint\nAssertion Classifier]
[0m[49m[39m  135, 137[0m:[39m[49m     D -->|Assertion Labels| B
[0m[49m[39m  136, 138[0m:[39m[49m     B -->|Store Results| E[DynamoDB\nAnnotated Entities]
[0m[49m[39m  137, 139[0m:[39m[49m     E -->|Query| F[Downstream:\nCDS, Quality, Research]
