[0m[49m[39m  163, 166[0m:[39m[49m |------------|------|
[0m[49m[39m  164, 167[0m:[39m[49m | **Amazon Comprehend Medical** | Entity extraction with basic trait detection (negation) |
[0m[49m[39m  165, 168[0m:[39m[49m | **Amazon SageMaker** | Hosts custom assertion classification model (fine-tuned transformer) |
[0m[49m[39m  166, 169[0m:[39m[49m | **Amazon S3** | Stores clinical notes, training data, and model artifacts |
[0m[49m[39m  167, 170[0m:[39m[49m | **AWS Lambda** | Orchestrates the extraction-classification pipeline |
[0m[49m[39m  168, 171[0m:[39m[49m | **Amazon DynamoDB** | Stores assertion-annotated entities for downstream query |
[0m[49m[39m  169, 172[0m:[39m[49m | **AWS KMS** | Manages encryption keys for all data stores |
